Text: She expects a cut of 25 basis point, taking the fed funds target rate range to 1.75 to 2.0%, following the last quarter point cut on July 31.
Cause: She expects a cut of 25 basis point
Effect: taking the fed funds target rate range to 1.75 to 2.0%, following the last quarter point cut on July 31.
